{{Top|leg}}
'''Bulior Repulsor Systems''' was a [[New Republic/Legends|New Republic]] corporation that developed a [[Starfighter/Legends|starfighter]] crash-restraint system suitable for installation into small [[Cockpit/Legends|cockpits]]. Small [[Repulsorlift/Legends|repulsorlift]] units would hold the [[Pilot/Legends|pilot]] in an invisible cocoon if his [[Starship/Legends|starship]] crashed. The corporation got a boost in the public relations sector when [[Derek Klivian/Legends|Derek Klivian]], the famous [[Rogue Squadron/Legends|Rogue Squadron]] pilot, endorsed the system.

